---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Stainless Steel Wire Pegs — All Products"
  description="Browse the full range of Wire Pegs stainless steel clothes pegs. Three grades of stainless steel, multiple sizes, and sock hangers. Buy at Biome."
>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-navy-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-500 mb-4">The Full Range</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy-900 leading-tight mb-6">Wire Pegs Products</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">Three grades of stainless steel. Multiple sizes. One purpose — the last pegs you'll ever buy.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-8 text-center">Which grade is right for you?</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-navy-900 text-white">
              <th class="p-4 text-left rounded-tl-xl">Grade</th>
              <th class="p-4 text-left">Best For</th>
              <th class="p-4 text-left">Leave Outside?</th>
              <th class="p-4 text-left rounded-tr-xl">Coastal Areas?</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-navy-100 bg-white">
              <td class="p-4 font-semibold text-navy-900">Grade 201</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-navy-600">Indoor use, bring pegs inside after washing</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-red-500">✗ No</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-red-500">✗ No</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-navy-100 bg-navy-50">
              <td class="p-4 font-semibold text-navy-900">Grade 304</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-navy-600">Outdoor use in most Australian conditions</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-teal-500">✓ Yes</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-red-500">✗ No</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-white">
              <td class="p-4 font-semibold text-navy-900">Grade 316</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-navy-600">Coastal homes, boats, harsh conditions</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-teal-500">✓ Yes</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-teal-500">✓ Yes</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="/which-peg" class="bg-teal-500 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-teal-700 transition-colors">Not sure? Use the Peg Finder →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-navy-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-8 text-center">Browse by product type</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy-100 p-8">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-500 mb-2">Grade 201</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">Standard Pegs</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm">Everyday stainless steel pegs for indoor use. Long lasting when cared for correctly.</p>
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <a href="/products/grade-201" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline underline-offset-4">Learn more</a>
            <a href="https://www.biome.com.au/collections/wire-pegs" target="_blank" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline underline-offset-4">Buy at Biome →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy-100 p-8">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-500 mb-2">Grade 304</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">Medium Grade Pegs</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm">Higher corrosion resistance for outdoor use. Twice the nickel content of Grade 201.</p>
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <a href="/products/grade-304" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline underline-offset-4">Learn more</a>
            <a href="https://www.biome.com.au/collections/wire-pegs" target="_blank" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline underline-offset-4">Buy at Biome →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy-100 p-8">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-500 mb-2">Grade 316</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">Marine Grade Pegs</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm">The ultimate peg. Used on boats and in construction. Will never rust, even near the ocean.</p>
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <a href="/products/grade-316" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline underline-offset-4">Learn more</a>
            <a href="https://www.biome.com.au/collections/wire-pegs" target="_blank" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline underline-offset-4">Buy at Biome →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy-100 p-8">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-500 mb-2">Specialty</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">Windy Conditions</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm">Thicker wire for extra grip on blustery days. Stays on the line when others blow off.</p>
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <a href="/products/windy-conditions" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline underline-offset-4">Learn more</a>
            <a href="https://www.biome.com.au/collections/wire-pegs" target="_blank" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline underline-offset-4">Buy at Biome →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy-100 p-8">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-500 mb-2">Specialty</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">Jumbo Pegs</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm">Our largest peg — perfect for pillows, doonas, and heavy items. Opens up to 20mm wide.</p>
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <a href="/products/jumbo" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline underline-offset-4">Learn more</a>
            <a href="https://www.biome.com.au/collections/wire-pegs" target="_blank" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline underline-offset-4">Buy at Biome →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy-100 p-8">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-500 mb-2">Accessory</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">Sock Hangers</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm">Stainless steel sock hangers that hold multiple pairs at once. Never lose a sock again.</p>
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <a href="/products/sock-hangers" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline underline-offset-4">Learn more</a>
            <a href="https://www.biome.com.au/collections/wire-pegs" target="_blank" class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-700 underline underline-offset-4">Buy at Biome →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-navy-900 text-white py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to order?</h2>
      <p class="text-navy-100 mb-8">All Wire Pegs products are available through Biome — Australia's leading eco store.</p>
      <a href="https://www.biome.com.au/collections/wire-pegs" target="_blank" class="bg-teal-500 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-teal-700 transition-colors">Shop at Biome →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>